@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Update button;
|System|
: (2) Display form to update Supplier information;
|User|
repeat: (3) Fill needed information;
: (4) Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: (5) Validate new information;
backward: (6) Show error message;
repeat while (Information valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (7) Update Supplier information to the database;
: (8) Update Supplier details screen;
stop
@enduml
